description: Fresh off a long trip, Princeton Price wants nothing more than to see his man and fall back into his comfortable bed, and Johnny B has made sure that this homecoming will be something special. He's decked out in his best looking outfit- his birthday suit- and waiting for Princeton with a welcoming sign and a come hither glance, but what Princeton is most happy about are those three little words Johnny whispers in his ear: 'Fuck me now!' Ever the dutiful boyfriend, Princeton is more than willing to oblige. There truly is no place like home!Enjoy!
title: Homecumming
